    "raw": "<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"kkp\">\n<style>\n.kkp{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto}\n.kkp .kkp-lead{font-size:1.18rem;line-height:1.5;max-width:62ch;margin:0 0 .4rem}\n.kkp .kkp-lead.kkp-kicker{font-weight:700}\n.kkp .kkp-label{font-size:.74rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;opacity:.55;margin:2rem 0 .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(210px,1fr));gap:1rem}\n.kkp .kkp-card{display:block;border:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);border-radius:11px;overflow:hidden;text-decoration:none;color:inherit;background:rgba(150,150,160,.05);transition:transform .15s ease,border-color .15s ease}\n.kkp .kkp-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);border-color:#e5462e}\n.kkp .kkp-card img,.kkp .kkp-ph{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover;display:block}\n.kkp .kkp-ph{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#23232e 0%,#3a2230 100%)}\n.kkp .kkp-txt{padding:.7rem .8rem .85rem}\n.kkp .kkp-title{font-weight:700;font-size:.96rem;line-height:1.25}\n.kkp .kkp-sub{font-size:.8rem;opacity:.68;margin-top:.28rem;line-height:1.35}\n.kkp .kkp-cta{margin-top:2.4rem;padding-top:1.1rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(150,150,160,.22);font-size:1.02rem}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a{color:#e5462e;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none}\n.kkp .kkp-cta a:hover{text-decoration:underline}\n</style>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-lead kkp-kicker\">I show up.</p>\n<p class=\"kkp-lead\">To the meetups, the hackathons, the film festivals, and the big global conferences that land in our backyard. Usually with my neck out and a point of view. These are the recaps and survival guides. What happened in the room, who was building, and what it means for the rest of us.</p>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">Web Summit Vancouver</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2026/05/07/web-summit-vancouver-2026/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/web-summit-vancouver-2026.jpg?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Web Summit 2026\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Web Summit 2026</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">The community shows up. So should the public metrics.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/04/13/web-summit-vancouver-2025-survival-guide/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/wsv2025-survival.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"2025 survival guide\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">2025 survival guide</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">A protocol shift rooted in justice and gentle refusal.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2024/09/05/the-outsiders-insider-guide-to-web-summit-vancouver/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Copy-of-Copy-of-AI-Immortality-w-Guy-Kawasaki-4.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Outsider's insider guide\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Outsider's insider guide</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">What it really means for our ecosystem.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"kkp-label\">Hackathons and festivals</div>\n<div class=\"kkp-grid\">\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/03/06/data-storytelling-hackathon-where-ai-meets-art-and-data-sings-its-truth/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/cant-talk-vanAI-hackathon.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Data Storytelling Hackathon\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Data Storytelling Hackathon</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Where AI meets art and data sings.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2025/03/20/is-a-hotdog-a-sandwich-vancouver-aidata-storytelling-hackathon-w-andrew-reid/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Hackathon-Data-Storytelling-YouTube-Thumbnail.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Is a hotdog a sandwich?\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Is a hotdog a sandwich?</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Planning the most ambitious AI hackathon.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2024/05/25/ai-in-filmmaking-at-the-yorkton-film-festival/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-sxsw2024-1-1.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"AI in filmmaking\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">AI in filmmaking</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">At the Yorkton Film Festival.</div></div></a>\n<a class=\"kkp-card\" href=\"https://kriskrug.co/2024/05/25/lisa-jacksons-wilfred-buck-documentary-premier-at-the-yorkton-film-festival/\"><img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/kriskrug.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-Copy-of-sxsw2024-2.png?resize=640,400&ssl=1\" alt=\"Wilfred Buck premiere\"/><div class=\"kkp-txt\"><div class=\"kkp-title\">Wilfred Buck premiere</div><div class=\"kkp-sub\">Lisa Jackson's cosmic documentary.</div></div></a>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"kkp-cta\">Browse the full <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/category/events-reports/\">Events and Reports</a> archive, or <a href=\"https://kriskrug.co/speaking/\">book me for your event</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<!-- /wp:html -->",
